- General way to make a new page is:
	1. Create the new file under the pages directory.
	2. Create a new case statement on the switch/case statement in default.php. (script in html head)
	3. Under the case statement, set the $headerText and $articleSource variables
	4. Create a list item and link/anchor directly in html in the <nav> element for regular user item, or
		in php (for admin items) in the head script to link to the new file.
		
This is a work in progress.

